        <li>The Customer is responsible for contacting the storage facility prior to pick-up to verify the unit(s) are accessible. If the Customer fails to verify accessibility and the unit is not accessible upon arrival, the Company will not be liable for any costs incurred, including dry-run fees.</li>
        <li>The Company provides seven (7) calendar days of free storage. After the free period elapses, a daily storage fee of $10.00 per day applies until the unit is picked up and out-gated.</li>
        <li>If the unit is not picked up within fourteen (14) calendar days, the Company may cancel the order and retract the release information at its discretion.</li>
